    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Cavalier/Samurai Order Abilitiy</strong><br/><br/><p>At 8th level, the cavalier may select a terrain type from the ranger Favored Terrains table. As a standard action, he can shout orders that grant all allies within 60 feet a competence bonus equal to his Charisma modifier on initiative checks and Knowledge (geography), Perception, and Survival checks while they are in this terrain for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 his cavalier level. At 12th level and every four levels thereafter, the cavalier may select a new terrain type that this ability can affect.</p>",
